Go to Jenkins UI
Install nodeJS plugin which has NPM in built.
Restart Jenkins 
Go to -> Manage Jenkins -> Global tool configuration -> Add NodeJS
Create a new Free style job with the below settings: 
 git: https://github.com/wardviaene/docker-demo/
 Build: Execute shell with the command npm install
 Build environment : Provide node & NPM path
Save and build the job  
